  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Take on the mob! The ultimate six exciting action sequences put you in control of Elliot Ness's elite squad of crime-busters. Alleyway shootouts, the Border Raid, the Railway Station confrontation and Warehouse bust, culminating in the thrilling denouement of a rooftop duel as you re-live the knife-edge existence of Ness in his stuggle against the retribution of Capone! The Untouchables - live an American legend!",
